lead_paragraph: Pakistan captain Misbah-ul-Haq hailed Asad Shafiq's defiant century as among the "classiest" he had ever seen after the knock of 137 all but drove Pakistan to a famous victory over Australia in the first test in Brisbane on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Misbah Hails 'Classy' Shafiq for Fighting Ton
